Package com.squareup.android

Enables Android applications to request payments through Square.  Start with Square. While the current version of Square for Android supports only one line item, this API allows for future support of multiple line items.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Bill A bill that can be paid using Square.
Bill.Builder Builds a bill.
Image An image locatable via a URL.
LineItem A line item in a bill.
LineItem.Builder Builds a line item.
Money A quantity of a specific currency.
Square Entry point of the Square for Android API.
 

Enum Summary
Currency Currency types supported by this API.
Image.Type Supported image types.
Square.InstallationStatus Status of the Square application on this device.
 

Exception Summary
ImageNotFoundException Thrown when an image can't be found.
 

Package com.squareup.android Description

Enables Android applications to request payments through Square.  Start with Square. While the current version of Square for Android supports only one line item, this API allows for future support of multiple line items.
